                        <p>Pharma City, CA 90210</p>
                        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Phone:</strong> <span>+1 555 987 6543</span></p>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <span>info@pharma.com</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="social-links d-flex mt-4">
                        <a href="https://x.com/pharma"><i class="bi bi-twitter-x"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://facebook.com/pharma"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://instagram.com/pharma"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
